text:
Earlier, the president gave them as souvenirs, and
we had them together with everyone who was there.

When I brewed tea for everyone, as a thank you,
they let me choose my favorite flavor.
I'm glad you're getting along with everyone.
Not just with Amana-chan and Tenka-chan...

Because everyone at 283 is wonderful,
I'm happy to be among them.

So,
the day when we all wear matching costumes...
Hehe, I'm really looking forward to it...!
